{"type": "article", "id": 28916, "title": "大理石吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-30T06:55:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021709241rViJTI5yzHkoY6P.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>由于石材的重量所带来的不安全感，大理石吊灯并不常见。<a href=\"http://atelieraltercn.com/home.htm\">Altelier Alter</a> 设计的这款名为 Suspended 的吊灯希望挑战人们对于这种材料的传统印象，悬浮在空中的姿态带给人一种轻盈的美，与大理石的厚重感形成了鲜明对比。当几组灯具高低不一地悬挂在房间中，起伏的折边看上去就像是白色的海浪。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170923N632RgxKdMeBFVSC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170923gpK1GulTWQUvEe8Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.628125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702170924BCcXZgeA0aQjtrVo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}